data.description:
Location Location Location! This property offers so many features, from the open floor plan to the beautiful backyard! The newly updated kitchen features new custom cabinets, a built in pantry, granite countertops, high end appliances and large center island perfect for entertaining. The sunroom off the kitchen leads outside to a huge deck and new above ground pool, a oversized patio perfect for all your summer events or relaxing! Open dining and living area leads you to the 3 main level bedrooms, master bedroom includes a large walk-in closet and handicap accessible bathroom with separate tub and shower. Downstairs you will find a finished basement with a custom bar, surround sound, full bathroom and 2 additional rooms ready for your personal touch to make an office or theatre! This property has so much to offer with some TLC you can make this house a home! You won't want to miss out! 

Property is being sold AS-IS, sellers to pay for no inspections or repairs.
